1️⃣ What is the request–response cycle?

👉 It is a communication model where a client sends an HTTP request to a server, and the server processes it and sends back an HTTP response.

2️⃣ What are the main components of an HTTP request?

👉

Method (GET, POST, etc.)
URL
Headers
Body (optional)
3️⃣ What are the parts of an HTTP response?

👉

Status code
Headers
Body
